<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pokémon Weather Adventure</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"> <!-- Link to your main stylesheet -->
  <style>
    .box {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      max-width: 800px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    /* Specific style for lists inside the .box class */
    .box ul {
      text-align: left;
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      max-width: fit-content;
    }

    .box ul li {
      margin-bottom: 10px; /* Add space between list items */
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="box">
      <h1 class="form-title">Welcome to Pokémon Weather App</h1>
      <p>Discover Pokémon based on the current weather conditions. Explore your personal Pokémon collection and track your search history.<br></p>
      <p>This app is designed to offer a unique Pokémon experience based on current weather conditions and your personal preferences.</p>
      <p><strong>Technologies & Skills Used:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Ruby on Rails:</strong> The core framework driving the application, ensuring a solid and scalable web experience.</li>
        <li><strong>OpenWeather API:</strong> Integrated to provide accurate weather data, allowing us to tailor Pokémon recommendations based on the weather.</li>
        <li><strong>Pokémon API:</strong> Fetches Pokémon data to provide a daily, weather-based Pokémon suggestion.</li>
        <li><strong>Devise:</strong> Powers secure user authentication and email recovery, making user management smooth and reliable.</li>
        <li><strong>ActiveRecord:</strong> Manages interactions with the database, including user Pokémon collections and search history.</li>
        <li><strong>RMagick:</strong> Handles Pokémon sprite images, ensuring that each Pokémon has a detailed and attractive image.</li>
        <li><strong>Turbo Rails:</strong> Enhances the user experience with real-time updates and minimal page refreshes.</li>
        <li><strong>SCSS:</strong> Used to style the app for a clean, modern look.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Features:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Dynamic Pokémon Recommendations:</strong> Discover Pokémon that match your local weather conditions, updated daily.</li>
        <li><strong>Personal Pokémon Collection:</strong> Manage and view your collection of Pokémon, complete with images and details.</li>
        <li><strong>Search History Tracking:</strong> View and sort your search history by number, height, and date/time.</li>
        <li><strong>Global Pokémon Tracking:</strong> Explore a comprehensive list of Pokémon and sort them based on various attributes.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </header>
  
  </main>
</body>
</html>